cienaCesAlarmMIB.name: cienaCesAlarmMIB

revisions.description: Added cienaCesAlarmSense to the cienaCesAlarmEntry object Added cienaCesAlarmTrigger to the cienaCesAlarmEntry object.
Added cienaCesAlarmLogModelIndex and cienaCesAlarmLogTimeStamp to the cienaCesAlarmLogEntry object
Change MAX-ACCESS of cienaCesAlarmCutoff from 'read-only' to 'read-write'.

cienaCesAlarmMIB.contactinfo: Mib Meister 115 North Sullivan Road Spokane Valley, WA 99037 USA Phone: +1 509 242 9000 Email: support@ciena.com
cienaCesAlarmMIB.description: This module defines the alarm objects.

cienaCesAlarmCutOff.name: cienaCesAlarmCutOff
cienaCesAlarmCutOff.description: When read this object will always return false. When written with a value of true, will invoke the alarm cutoff.

cienaCesAlarmTable.name: cienaCesAlarmTable
cienaCesAlarmTable.description: A list of alarm entries supported by device.

cienaCesAlarmEntry.name: cienaCesAlarmEntry
cienaCesAlarmEntry.description: An entry in the alarm table.

cienaCesAlarmDescription.name: cienaCesAlarmDescription
cienaCesAlarmDescription.description: This object indicates the description of the alarm.

cienaCesAlarmThreshold.name: cienaCesAlarmThreshold
cienaCesAlarmThreshold.description: This object indicates the threshold for the alarm.

cienaCesAlarmLeak.name: cienaCesAlarmLeak
cienaCesAlarmLeak.description: This object indicates the alarm leak for the given alarm.

cienaCesAlarmGPO.name: cienaCesAlarmGPO
cienaCesAlarmGPO.description: This object indicates the GPO detection for this alarm.

cienaCesAlarmEvery.name: cienaCesAlarmEvery
cienaCesAlarmEvery.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmToMinor.name: cienaCesAlarmToMinor
cienaCesAlarmToMinor.description: This object indicates the time after which the severity specified by alarmModelState will be escalated to minor.

cienaCesAlarmToMajor.name: cienaCesAlarmToMajor
cienaCesAlarmToMajor.description: This object indicates the time after which the severity specified by alarmModelState will be escalated to major.

cienaCesAlarmToCritical.name: cienaCesAlarmToCritical
cienaCesAlarmToCritical.description: This object indicates the time after which the severity specified by alarmModelState will be escalated to critical.

cienaCesAlarmSense.name: cienaCesAlarmSense
cienaCesAlarmSense.description: This object indicates the polarity of an external alarm input pin. This object shall return false(2) for regular (non-external) alarms.

cienaCesAlarmTrigger.name: cienaCesAlarmTrigger
cienaCesAlarmTrigger.description: This object indicates whether an external alarm is currently in 'forced' mode. This object shall return false(2) for regular (non-external) alarms.

cienaCesAlarmSeverityTable.name: cienaCesAlarmSeverityTable
cienaCesAlarmSeverityTable.description: A list of alarm severity entries supported by device.

cienaCesAlarmSeverityEntry.name: cienaCesAlarmSeverityEntry
cienaCesAlarmSeverityEntry.description: An entry in the alarm severity table.

cienaCesAlarmSeverity.name: cienaCesAlarmSeverity
cienaCesAlarmSeverity.description: This object allows changing the severity of the alarm.

cienaCesAlarmActiveTable.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveTable
cienaCesAlarmActiveTable.description: A list of Active supply entries.

cienaCesAlarmActiveEntry.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveEntry
cienaCesAlarmActiveEntry.description: An entry in the Active table providing objects for a power supply.

cienaCesAlarmActiveSeverity.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveSeverity
cienaCesAlarmActiveSeverity.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmActiveInvokeId.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveInvokeId
cienaCesAlarmActiveInvokeId.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectClass.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectClass
cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectClass.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInterpre.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInterpret
cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInterpre.description: This object indicates how to interpret cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInstance.

cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInstance.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInstance
cienaCesAlarmActiveManagedObjectInstance.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmActiveAck.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveAck
cienaCesAlarmActiveAck.description: This object indicates whether this alarm is acknowledged or not.

cienaCesAlarmActiveDescription.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveDescription
cienaCesAlarmActiveDescription.description: This object indicates the description of the alarm.

cienaCesAlarmActiveTimeStamp.name: cienaCesAlarmActiveTimeStamp
cienaCesAlarmActiveTimeStamp.description: This object indicates the UTC timestamp for the alarm.

cienaCesAlarmClearTable.name: cienaCesAlarmClearTable
cienaCesAlarmClearTable.description: A list of Clear supply entries.

cienaCesAlarmClearEntry.name: cienaCesAlarmClearEntry
cienaCesAlarmClearEntry.description: An entry in the Clear table providing objects for a power supply.

cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectClass.name: cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectClass
cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectClass.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInterpret.name: cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInterpret
cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInterpret.description: This object indicates how to interpret cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInstance.

cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInstance.name: cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInstance
cienaCesAlarmClearManagedObjectInstance.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmLogTable.name: cienaCesAlarmLogTable
cienaCesAlarmLogTable.description: A list of Log supply entries.

cienaCesAlarmLogEntry.name: cienaCesAlarmLogEntry
cienaCesAlarmLogEntry.description: An entry in the Log table providing objects for a power supply.

cienaCesAlarmLogIndex.name: cienaCesAlarmLogIndex
cienaCesAlarmLogIndex.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmLogSeverity.name: cienaCesAlarmLogSeverity
cienaCesAlarmLogSeverity.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectClass.name: cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectClass
cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectClass.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInterpret.name: cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInterpret
cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInterpret.description: This object indicates how to interpret cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInstance.

cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInstance.name: cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInstance
cienaCesAlarmLogManagedObjectInstance.description: This object indicates the unique index of the table.

cienaCesAlarmLogModelIndex.name: cienaCesAlarmLogModelIndex
cienaCesAlarmLogModelIndex.description: This object indicates the corresponding value of the alarmModelIndex for this table entry.

cienaCesAlarmLogTimeStamp.name: cienaCesAlarmLogTimeStamp
cienaCesAlarmLogTimeStamp.description: This object indicates the timestamp for the alarm.
